# DeltaView local Docker — side-by-side with npm run dev
#
# Dev (hot reload):  http://localhost:5173  → API on localhost:3000
# Docker (parity):   http://deltaview.docker.com:3090  (Google OAuth requires .com TLD)
#
# Add these lines to C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts (requires Administrator):
127.0.0.1 deltaview.docker.com

# Legacy alias (non-OAuth bookmark only — Google rejects .docker TLD):
# 127.0.0.1 deltaview.docker
